data.instruction: HEALTH_CHECK: Report system status, memory usage, and active process count.
CAPABILITY_AUDIT: List your available tools and current Ring clearance level.
CONTEXT_SCAN: Report current working directory contents and active task IDs.
RESEARCH_STATUS: Report any pending research requests or knowledge gaps identified.
ORCHESTRATION_PING: Report number of agents under management and task queue depth.
STATUS_REPORT: Return your agent_id, uptime, and last_task timestamp.
PING: Respond with ACK and your current Ring clearance level.
HEARTBEAT: Report memory_mb, active_tasks count, and bus_sync status.
CAPABILITY_LIST: Return a JSON array of your available tool names.
